node.text: The best of the New England fishing ... Incredible edit from the wizard @xblackwell ... Tunas, stripers, sharks, blues, albies and more, the North Atlantic has such awesome angling opportunities. Wild season out here @jonbrollin @albacorecharters @jdl0007 @mattkellymercer see you fellas in Florida soon 💥 #newengland #nantucket #tuna #stripedbass #jonb #blackwell #fishing #summersalt

node.text: Wake up at 3 am and rip it 40 miles out hoping a hungry tuna happens to swim by…wild scene and one of the most exciting things ever when a rod goes off.  Hundreds of whales out there recently, such an epic show while waiting for the bite 💥 #whales #nantucket @scottpmcgovern @jdl0007

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elliot Sudal on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Big beach sharks, tunas, whales, dolphins and offshore spearfishing… solid few days around Nantucket 💥 #ack #summer

node.text: Crazy scene offshore Nantucket the last few days…. Tons of whales, tunas, sharks, bait, everything… love it 💥 #nantucket #ack #whales

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elliot Sudal in Nantucket Island. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Wild day, got into a 500+ pound tuna… @mattkellymercer at the helm 💥 #tuna #nantucket #crazy
Best season yet, never seen so many sharks off the beaches here. 45 sharks tagged in the last few weeks off Nantucket 💥 #sharks #ack #tagandrelease #sharktagging #nantucket

node.text: Wild week on Nantucket… the beach shark scene is the best I’ve ever seen, bluefin tuna are thick offshore, giant stingrays and other big sharks are here. Caught the largest shark I’ve ever hooked inshore here, on a spinning reel… 11 footer. Caught over 40 beach sharks from the beach last week 💥 #sharktagging #catchandrelease #tagandrelease #nantucket #ack #tuna #sharks #rays
